# ============================================================================
# Ten Lifetimes — PUBLIC production repo.
# Belt-and-suspenders: the repo is assembled from a docs-only tree, but these
# rules guarantee no media or private assets are ever committed.
# ============================================================================

# --- Media: audio / video / images / project files ---
*.mp3
*.wav
*.flac
*.aif
*.aiff
*.mp4
*.mov
*.mkv
*.avi
*.webm
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png
*.webp
*.gif
*.tif
*.tiff
*.bmp
*.psd
*.ai
*.aep
*.prproj
*.zip
*.7z
*.rar

# --- Private asset folders (reference photos, masters, master refs) ---
01_Reference_Gary/
02_Reference_Jen/
03_Couple_Photos/
16_Master_References/

# --- Per-chapter media subfolders ---
*/Stills/
*/Motion/
*/Final/
*/References/

# --- EXCEPTION: review dailies are intentionally PUBLIC for Gemini GVR ---
# EP decision 2026-06-26: generated review stills are committed to 12_Dailies/
# so the VFX reviewer (Gemini) can access them from the repo.
!12_Dailies/**/*.png
!12_Dailies/**/*.jpg
!12_Dailies/**/*.jpeg

# --- EXCEPTION: Production_History is the public ILM-style learning archive ---
# EP decision 2026-06-26 (full archive): superseded/rejected renders are KEPT and
# published with their .md provenance as institutional memory for Continuum.
!13_Production_History/**/*.png
!13_Production_History/**/*.jpg
!13_Production_History/**/*.jpeg

# --- GitHub Asset Canon (Director, 2026-06-26): GitHub is the FULL production history. ---
# All GENERATED assets + Dossiers are public across these stage folders. NON-generated
# source assets (real source photos, music masters, stems, .prproj) stay NAS-private
# (still covered by the media rules above). Review Queue = visible dailies, not canon.
!12_Review_Queue/**/*.png
!12_Review_Queue/**/*.jpg
!12_Review_Queue/**/*.jpeg
!14_Selected/**/*.png
!14_Selected/**/*.jpg
!14_Selected/**/*.jpeg
!15_Final/**/*.png
!15_Final/**/*.jpg
!15_Final/**/*.jpeg

# --- EXCEPTION: Master Identity Sheets (Gemini directive, 2026-06-27) ---
# The locked "Source of Truth" face anchors (Gary/Jen per era). Generated from the
# real photos via nb2 edit-restyle; conditioned into every scene. Public.
!00_Identity_Master/**/*.png
!00_Identity_Master/**/*.jpg
!00_Identity_Master/**/*.jpeg

# --- EXCEPTION: Canonical Costume Assets (CRE-005, 2026-06-27) ---
# Per-era costume sheets, conditioned on the CCA faces. Public, like the identity sheets.
!00_Costume_Master/**/*.png
!00_Costume_Master/**/*.jpg
!00_Costume_Master/**/*.jpeg

# --- Tooling / environments / OS cruft ---
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# never commit credentials
*.key
Gemini.key
gemini.key

# motion clips in stage folders (mirror the still exceptions)
!13_Production_History/**/*.mp4
!12_Review_Queue/**/*.mp4
!14_Selected/**/*.mp4
!15_Final/**/*.mp4
